<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>An Chaothernach</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #2c3e50;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    header {
      background: #34495e;
      color: white;
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    header p {
      opacity: 0.9;
      font-size: 1.1em;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.6em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #2c3e50;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: #555;
    }

    .section {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .download {
      background: #ecf0f1;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .platform {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border-left: 3px solid #3498db;
    }

    .platform h3 {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #2c3e50;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .steps {
      margin: 16px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: #555;
    }

    .steps li {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }

    .note {
      background: #fff9e6;
      border-left: 3px solid #f39c12;
      padding: 12px;
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-size: 0.95em;
      color: #666;
    }

    .code {
      background: #2c3e50;
      color: #ecf0f1;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin: 12px 0;
    }

    footer {
      background: #ecf0f1;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #7f8c8d;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #3498db;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header h1 {
        font-size: 2em;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>An Chaothernach</h1>
      <p>Language Islands for Irish Learners</p>
    </header>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="section">
        <h2>About</h2>
        <p>
          An Chaothernach is a mobile app for learning Irish through "language islands" -
          small collections of memorizable sentences about specific topics.
        </p>
        <p>
          Based on Boris Shekhtman's method, the app helps you build fluency by creating
          pre-prepared speeches you can fall back on in conversation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="download">
        <h2>Get the App</h2>

        <div class="platform">
          <h3>iOS</h3>
          <ol class="steps">
            <li>Install Expo Go from the App Store</li>
            <li>Scan the QR code with your camera</li>
            <li>Open the link in Expo Go</li>
          </ol>
          <div class="note">
            Development build - requires Expo Go app
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="platform">
          <h3>Android</h3>
          <ol class="steps">
            <li>Install Expo Go from Google Play</li>
            <li>Open Expo Go and scan the QR code</li>
          </ol>
          <div class="note">
            Development build - requires Expo Go app
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="platform">
          <h3>Development</h3>
          <div class="code">cd mobile<br>npm install<br>npx expo start</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul class="steps">
          <li>Create islands using voice input (English)</li>
          <li>Listen with native Irish speech synthesis (Ulster/Munster)</li>
          <li>Study topic-specific vocabulary</li>
          <li>Practice with AI conversation mode</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Technology</h2>
        <ul class="steps">
          <li>React Native + Expo</li>
          <li>OpenAI GPT-4 & Whisper</li>
          <li>Abair.ie speech synthesis</li>
          <li>TCD Phonetics speech recognition</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <p>
        Created by Seosamh Ó Cathail<br>
        <a href="https://github.com/seosamh">github.com/seosamh</a>
      </p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
